      <title>馬斯克的 X Corp 對駁回針對反仇恨組織的訴訟提出上訴</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/musks-x-corp-appeals-dismissal-lawsuit-against-anti-hate-group-2024-04-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[馬斯克(Elon Musk) 的X 對非營利組織反擊數字仇恨中心(Center for Countering Digital Hate) 的訴訟被駁回提出上訴，該中心指責埃隆·馬斯克(Elon Musk) 讓仇恨言論在曾經被稱為Twitter 的社交媒體平台上傳播。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/musks-x-corp-appeals-dismissal-lawsuit-against-anti-hate-group-2024-04-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 23:06:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
